_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper

# NCrunch
_NCrunch_*/
.*crunch*.

# Cobertura / análisis
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
coverage/
.coverage/
.nyc_output/
.sonarqube/

##############################
